    "description": "本課程幫助學生建立能正確書寫英文句子，進而針對特定主題書寫英文段落來表達個人觀點。<br>This is a writing course to help students develop sentences to form paragraphs in order to participate in EMI classes. Students will develop and link a variety of English sentences to form a simple cohesive paragraph, write realistic short writing assignments and gain self-editing experience.<br>",
